---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
import SkillsGrid from "./SkillsGrid.astro";

const heading = "About";
---

<section id="about" class="px-4">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <SectionHeader heading={heading} />
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p>I build responsive, dynamic web apps with <span class="text-emerald-200/80 font-medium">Astro</span>, <span class="text-emerald-200/80 font-medium">TailwindCSS</span> and <span class="text-emerald-200/80 font-medium">React</span>—focusing on clean code, intuitive design, and great user experiences.</p>
      <p>Eager to contribute to dynamic projects while continuously expanding my skills in building scalable and responsive web applications.</p>
      <p>When I'm not deep in development mode, you'll either find me on the tennis court, running along scenic trails, or enjoying a well-earned rest day—while humbly accepting that my pets are the true project managers at home.</p>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">My Skills</h3>
    <p>I'm a passionate learner and these are some of the technologies and tools I've used often. </p>
    <SkillsGrid />
  </div>
</section>
